"500\" height=\"341\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236763\" /></noscript></a><br />\n感谢所有陪我走到现在的人，尤其感谢打算仍然硬着头皮陪我走下去的人。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/22221.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/22221.jpg\" alt=\"2222\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236764\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/22221.jpg\" alt=\"2222\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236764\" /></noscript></a><br />\n去见你喜欢的人，去做你想做的事，就把这些当成你青春里最后的任性。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2223.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2223.jpg\" alt=\"2223\" width=\"500\" height=\"665\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236765\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2223.jpg\" alt=\"2223\" width=\"500\" height=\"665\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236765\" /></noscript></a><br />\n因为只有在年轻时灿烂燃烧过，年老后才会变成恬静有气质不计较的老太太。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2224.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2224.jpg\" alt=\"2224\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236766\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2224.jpg\" alt=\"2224\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236766\" /></noscript></a><br />\n信任就如同一个一岁小孩的感觉，当你将他扔向天空的时候，他会笑，因为他知道你会接住他，这就是信任。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2225.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2225.jpg\" alt=\"2225\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236767\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2225.jpg\" alt=\"2225\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236767\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我疯过，傻过，执着过，坚持过，忍耐过，到最后还是一个人过。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2226.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2226.jpg\" alt=\"2226\" width=\"500\" height=\"313\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236768\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2226.jpg\" alt=\"2226\" width=\"500\" height=\"313\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236768\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我们真的要过了很久很久，才能够明白，自己真正怀念的，到底是怎样的人，怎样的事。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2227.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2227.jpg\" alt=\"2227\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236769\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2227.jpg\" alt=\"2227\" width=\"500\" height=\"400\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236769\" /></noscript></a><br />\n对一座城的留恋其实是留恋那里的人和事，更多的是沉淀在那座城里自己最好的年华。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2228.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2228.jpg\" alt=\"2228\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236770\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2228.jpg\" alt=\"2228\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236770\" /></noscript></a><br />\n爱情一定是婚姻的前提，而珍惜，才是携手鬓白的那份必须的执念。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2229.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2229.jpg\" alt=\"2229\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236771\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2229.jpg\" alt=\"2229\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236771\" /></noscript></a><br />\n试着用左手握住右手, 给了自己最简单的温暖，不会再奢求别人的给予, 开始学着自己给自己。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2230.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2230.jpg\" alt=\"2230\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236772\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2230.jpg\" alt=\"2230\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236772\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1703),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>时间真的很好，让痛的不再痛了，让放不下的放下了。<br />\n<span id=\"more-236562\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1281.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1281.jpg\" alt=\"1281\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236563\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1281.jpg\" alt=\"1281\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236563\" /></noscript></a><br />\n幸福就是每一个微小愿望的达成。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1282.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1282.jpg\" alt=\"1282\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236564\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1282.jpg\" alt=\"1282\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236564\" /></noscript></a><br />\n做自己生命的主角，而不是别人生命中的看客。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1283.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1283.jpg\" alt=\"1283\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236565\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1283.jpg\" alt=\"1283\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236565\" /></noscript></a><br />\n爱是一种遇见，不能等待，也不能准备 。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1284.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1284.jpg\" alt=\"1284\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236566\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1284.jpg\" alt=\"1284\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236566\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生命苦短，你应该过得开心些。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1285.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1285.jpg\" alt=\"1285\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236567\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1285.jpg\" alt=\"1285\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236567\" /></noscript></a><br />\n有时候，坚持了你最不想干的事情之后，会得到你最想要的东西。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1286.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1286.jpg\" alt=\"1286\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236568\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1286.jpg\" alt=\"1286\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236568\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果你想要你从未拥有过的东西，那么你必须去做你从未做过的事。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1287.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1287.jpg\" alt=\"1287\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236569\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1287.jpg\" alt=\"1287\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236569\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人们为什么轻言放弃？因为他们只是看到前方路途遥远，而忘记了身后的一路坚持。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1288.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1288.jpg\" alt=\"1288\" width=\"500\" height=\"369\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236570\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1288.jpg\" alt=\"1288\" width=\"500\" height=\"369\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236570\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一念繁华一念灰； 一念成悦，处处繁华处处锦；一念成执，寸寸相思寸寸灰。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1289.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1289.jpg\" alt=\"1289\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236571\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1289.jpg\" alt=\"1289\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236571\" /></noscript></a><br />\n慢下来，静下来，听一听花开的声音，告诉自己，生活，真好！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1290.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1290.jpg\" alt=\"1290\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236572\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1290.jpg\" alt=\"1290\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236572\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1704),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>做一个淡然女子，飘忽人际中，置身世相外，拒万般诱惑，赢一人之心；做一个静默女子，浅笑袪千愁，轻语醉春秋，虽不善言辞，亦自成风景；做一个浓情女子，寂时似禅定，情开如烈火，爱就梦一场，别恨只道无；做一个寒梅女子，只为暖冬，无意争春，惟愿走过，不求来过。<br />\n<span id=\"more-236533\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4911.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4911.jpg\" alt=\"491\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236535\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4911.jpg\" alt=\"491\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236535\" /></noscript></a><br />\n旅途中遇到的每一个人，每一件事，每一处美丽的景色，我带不走，也留不下，来了即是来了，走也就走了，但这些都有可能成为一生中难忘的记忆。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4921.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4921.jpg\" alt=\"492\" width=\"500\" height=\"270\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236536\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4921.jpg\" alt=\"492\" width=\"500\" height=\"270\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236536\" /></noscript></a><br />\n再坚强的人，心里都一定有那么一些弱点，一触就碎，一碰就痛。因为不想受伤，我们戴上面具，穿上武裝，设法把自己脆弱的一面藏起來。我们愈不敢面对伤痛，被刺伤的时候，伤口就愈痛。最不容易受伤的人，不是最坚强的人，而是最坦诚面对自己的人。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4931.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4931.jpg\" alt=\"493\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236537\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4931.jpg\" alt=\"493\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236537\" /></noscript></a><br />\n都说时光飞逝。其实时间一直都在，只是自己的心在变，情在变。人说抵挡不过时间，其实是时间抵挡不过我们的善变。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4941.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4941.jpg\" alt=\"494\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236538\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4941.jpg\" alt=\"494\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236538\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一直以为幸福在远方，在可以追逐的未来。后来才发现，那些拥抱过的人，握过的手、唱过的歌、流过的泪、爱过的人、所谓的曾经，就是幸福。在无数的夜里，说过的话、打过的电话，思念过的人、流过的眼泪！看见的或看不见的感动，我们都曾经过，然后在时间的穿梭中，一切成为了永恒！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4951.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4951.jpg\" alt=\"495\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236539\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4951.jpg\" alt=\"495\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236539\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一个人至少拥有一个梦想，有一个理由去坚强。心若没有栖息的地方，到哪里都是在流浪。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4961.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4961.jpg\" alt=\"496\" width=\"500\" height=\"502\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236540\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4961.jpg\" alt=\"496\" width=\"500\" height=\"502\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236540\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生活总和我们开着玩笑，你期待什么，什么就会离你越远；你执着谁，就会被谁伤害得最深。没有结局的感情，总要结束；不能拥有的人，总会忘记。有些事注定成为故事，有些人注定成为故人，有些路注定要一个人走。既不回头，何必不忘。既然无缘，何必誓言。这个世界那么脏，谁有资格说悲伤</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4971.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4971.jpg\" alt=\"497\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236541\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4971.jpg\" alt=\"497\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236541\" /></noscript></a><br />\n那时候，未来遥远而没有形状，梦想还不知道该叫什么名字。 我常常一个人，走很长的路，在起风的时候觉得自己像一片落叶。仰望星空，我想知道：有人正从世界的某个地方朝我走来吗？像光那样，从一颗星到达另外一颗星。 后来，你出现了，又离开了。我们等候着青春，却错过了彼此……</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4981.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4981.jpg\" alt=\"498\" width=\"500\" height=\"471\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236542\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4981.jpg\" alt=\"498\" width=\"500\" height=\"471\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236542\" /></noscript></a><br />\n小心你的思想，因为它不久就会成为你的行为，小心你的行动，因为它不久就成为你的习惯，小心你的习惯，因为它不久就会成为你的品格——我的心中每天开出一朵花</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4991.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4991.jpg\" alt=\"499\" width=\"500\" height=\"339\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236543\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/4991.jpg\" alt=\"499\" width=\"500\" height=\"339\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236543\" /></noscript></a><br />\n面对失败和挫折，一笑而过是一种乐观自信，然后重振旗鼓，这是一种勇气；面对误解和仇恨，一笑而过是一种坦然宽容，然后保持本色，这是一种达观；面对赞扬和激励，一笑而过是一种谦虚清醒，然后不断进取，这是一种力量；面对烦恼和忧愁，一笑而过是一种平和释然，然后努力化解，这是一种境界。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5001.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5001.jpg\" alt=\"500\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236544\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/5001.jpg\" alt=\"500\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236544\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1705),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>如果，所有的伤痕都能够痊愈； 如果，所有的真心都能够换来真意；如果，所有的相信都能够坚持；如果，所有的情感都能够完美；如果，依然能相遇在某座城，单纯的微笑，微微的幸福，肆意的拥抱， 该多好。可是真的只是如果。<br />\n<span id=\"more-236520\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/51.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/51.jpg\" alt=\"51\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236521\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/51.jpg\" alt=\"51\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236521\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/52.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/52.jpg\" alt=\"52\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236522\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/52.jpg\" alt=\"52\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236522\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/53.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/53.jpg\" alt=\"53\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236523\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/53.jpg\" alt=\"53\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236523\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/54.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/54.jpg\" alt=\"54\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236524\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/54.jpg\" alt=\"54\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236524\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/55.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/55.jpg\" alt=\"55\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236525\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/55.jpg\" alt=\"55\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236525\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/56.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/56.jpg\" alt=\"56\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236526\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/56.jpg\" alt=\"56\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236526\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/57.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/57.jpg\" alt=\"57\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236527\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/57.jpg\" alt=\"57\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236527\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/58.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/58.jpg\" alt=\"58\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236528\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/58.jpg\" alt=\"58\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236528\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/59.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/59.jpg\" alt=\"59\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236529\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/59.jpg\" alt=\"59\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236529\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/60.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/60.jpg\" alt=\"60\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236530\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/60.jpg\" alt=\"60\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236530\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1706),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>傍晚，从海滩边走回到站台的时候，我遇见了一个背影。</p>\n<p>那个背影，很熟悉，又很陌生，想了很长时间，就是没想到会是谁的背影这么深刻在我脑海里。<br />\n<span id=\"more-236633\"></span><br />\n坐上公车的时候，脑海里依旧是那个背影，徘徘徊徊，走走停停，冷不丁，我想起来，模糊又清晰。</p>\n<p>那个时候，情窦都没有，更别提有初开。他是比我高一年级的学生，他有一个很好听的名字，吴梦凡，当我知道他名字的时候，他马上就快毕业了吧。第一次看见他的时候，是在下楼梯的时候，我不小心撞到他的肩膀，他很随意的笑了一下，然后走开了，当时，心里很暖，因为他笑起来很好看，很舒心，再后来能遇见他的机会很少，因为他在三楼，而我在一楼。</p>\n<p>慢慢的，就淡忘了那一次的遇见与擦肩。</p>\n<p>很快的，初三模拟考的日子就要来了，许多接近尾声的秘密也都一个个见光了，当再次听到宿舍女生讨论某某班谁谁谁很帅，谁喜欢谁谁谁的时候，我才知道原来他的名字那么好听，就如同他笑起来那么好看一样。他也是班里的学习委员，也是那一帮帅哥里的一分子，但他很斯文，出现在我面前的时候，我觉得就像太阳一样，但那时候，我还不知道什么是喜欢，算是完全用崇拜的眼光去认真对待一份在心里面从滋生到枯萎的心情。</p>\n<p>他毕业考试的时候，我在放假，玩的不亦乐乎。当我考试的时候，我才想起来，他已经考过试，已经要离开这所学校，而我就再也不会见到他，后来就真的没再见到了。</p>\n<p>我想，从头到尾，我连一句话都没和他说上，就只是知道他有一个很好听的名字，还有一个留给我唯一一个很舒心的微笑。</p>\n<p>时间过去很久，久到我把他也遗忘了很多年，如果不是今天会再次遇到和他相似的背影，我想这个遗忘它还在持续。</p>\n<p>我在想，如果当时我的情窦初开的早点，我一定会鼓起勇气去追他，因为他在我的印象里，很美好，很美好。</p>\n<p>时间飞快，白驹过隙，我想你我身边的人换了也有好几番了吧，你现在有喜欢的人吗？你喜欢的人喜欢你吗？</p>\n<p>希望你幸福，深藏在岁月里与脑海里最美好的男孩。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-la