t/uploads/2013/10/18041.jpg\" alt=\"1804\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236487\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18041.jpg\" alt=\"1804\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236487\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18051.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18051.jpg\" alt=\"1805\" width=\"500\" height=\"351\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236488\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18051.jpg\" alt=\"1805\" width=\"500\" height=\"351\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236488\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18061.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18061.jpg\" alt=\"1806\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236489\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18061.jpg\" alt=\"1806\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236489\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18071.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18071.jpg\" alt=\"1807\" width=\"500\" height=\"362\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236490\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18071.jpg\" alt=\"1807\" width=\"500\" height=\"362\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236490\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18081.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18081.jpg\" alt=\"1808\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236491\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18081.jpg\" alt=\"1808\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236491\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18091.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18091.jpg\" alt=\"1809\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236492\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18091.jpg\" alt=\"1809\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236492\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18101.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18101.jpg\" alt=\"1810\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236493\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/18101.jpg\" alt=\"1810\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236493\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1711),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>阔别已久，回来了。­</p>\n<p>清晨的第一缕光线透过窗帘的缝隙洋洋洒洒的轻触我的眼睑。来到阳台，淅淅沥沥的雨点拼命往下掉，宣泄着一冬的枯寂所带来的灰色伤心的曲调。­<br />\n<span id=\"more-236356\"></span><br />\n下雨了？­</p>\n<p>下雨了！­</p>\n<p>于是，视线随着雨帘渐渐变远，幾棵樹籠罩其間。愕然發現，木棉樹上的一片嫣紅不知何時已被一片翠綠取代？­</p>\n<p>感嘆從心中發出，原來一切都在不知不覺間發生改變。來不及適應，於是低頭尋找是否有落花的痕跡，卻已是虛無。只能再次驚嘆時間的流逝。­</p>\n<p>仿佛是煎熬，又仿佛是等待，新綠的葉子在雨中搖曳著，接受天地的洗禮，洗去了幼嫩，取而代之的是堅挺。然而畢竟是新長得，在雨的冲刷下依然無法與周圍的樹木的葉子青翠欲滴相比。周圍的樹，他們的葉子已經經歷了比木棉術葉子更長的日子。在密集的雨中，依然高傲地挺著高大的身軀，一片片葉子如刀鋒般切斷雨線。在樹群的不屑中，寥寥幾棵木棉術的葉子卻無法抵抗雨的強勢攻擊，只能無奈的低頭，然而他們卻不屈服，那股堅韌依在。­</p>\n<p>偶而一瞥，無法看出那層經開出绚爛花朵的木棉術在哪，甚至旁邊低矮的灌木也綠的比他們顯眼，在這一丛中，木棉術如此平凡，平凡到我們忽略了他們。­</p>\n<p>回想，曾經滿樹的紅花向火焰一般向人們展示了他的熱情，他的桀傲。如今卻以最謙卑的姿態呈現。這種天與地的差别，真的無法想象，木棉術竟有這樣隱忍之心。­</p>\n<p>或許他在等待下一次棉絮飄飛，讓人們再次將焦點集中在他們身上，驚嘆他們在紅綠的變幻中，還有一片純潔的白！­<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/p