223_a27ecb01d2_b.jpg\' title=\'6149025223_a27ecb01d2_b\'><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/6149025223_a27ecb01d2_b-190x256.jpg\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"6149025223_a27ecb01d2_b\" /><noscript><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/6149025223_a27ecb01d2_b-190x256.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"6149025223_a27ecb01d2_b\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1712),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>单纯喜欢你的人，他看到的是你的现在；真正爱你的人，要和你走的是未来！真正的爱情，不是某一个时刻的承诺和表白，而是之后一起走过的岁月！<br />\n<span id=\"more-236323\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1461.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1461.jpg\" alt=\"1461\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236324\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1461.jpg\" alt=\"1461\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236324\" /></noscript></a><br />\n无论吵闹多少次 说多少伤人的话 最后还是会因为舍不得对方而和好如初 这种感觉真好<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1462.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1462.jpg\" alt=\"1462\" width=\"500\" height=\"401\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236325\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1462.jpg\" alt=\"1462\" width=\"500\" height=\"401\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236325\" /></noscript></a><br />\n与其在风雨中逃避，不如在雷电中舞蹈，即便淋得透湿，也是领略生命的快意。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1463.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1463.jpg\" alt=\"1463\" width=\"500\" height=\"442\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236326\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1463.jpg\" alt=\"1463\" width=\"500\" height=\"442\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236326\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人间的事往往如此，当时提起痛不欲生，几年之后，也不过是一场回忆而已。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1464.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1464.jpg\" alt=\"1464\" width=\"500\" height=\"362\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236327\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1464.jpg\" alt=\"1464\" width=\"500\" height=\"362\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236327\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人生这部大戏，一旦拉开序幕，不管你如何怯场，都得演到戏的结尾。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1465.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1465.jpg\" alt=\"1465\" width=\"500\" height=\"326\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236328\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1465.jpg\" alt=\"1465\" width=\"500\" height=\"326\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236328\" /></noscript></a><br />\n坚强的内心，往往会被一句简单的安慰打败，然后泪流满面。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1466.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1466.jpg\" alt=\"1466\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236329\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1466.jpg\" alt=\"1466\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236329\" /></noscript></a><br />\n做自己的梦，去自己想去的地方，做自己想做的人，因为生命只有一次，机会只有一回。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1467.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1467.jpg\" alt=\"1467\" width=\"500\" height=\"730\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236330\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1467.jpg\" alt=\"1467\" width=\"500\" height=\"730\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236330\" /></noscript></a><br />\n让来的人来，让去的人去。顺其自然，是对生活最大的成全。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1468.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1468.jpg\" alt=\"1468\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236331\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1468.jpg\" alt=\"1468\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236331\" /></noscript></a><br />\n有时候，惟有一场眼泪，我们才彻底清晰了视线。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1469.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1469.jpg\" alt=\"1469\" width=\"500\" height=\"369\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236332\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1469.jpg\" alt=\"1469\" width=\"500\" height=\"369\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236332\" /></noscript></a><br />\n要相信，这个世界里美好总要多过阴暗，欢乐总要多过苦难，还有很多事，值得你一如既往的相信。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1470.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1470.jpg\" alt=\"1470\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236333\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1470.jpg\" alt=\"1470\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236333\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1713),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>若人生只有初见； 我想我们应该去学会淡淡的对待身边的每次 。</p>\n<p>走走停停；反反复复 。还是会失望的回到原来的地点；还是想找回到最初那个自己。<br />\n <span id=\"more-236179\"></span><br />\n那些渲染过的温馨画面浮现眼前;时光转不断；它在拼命的逼你回忆曾经的一切。你想去忘记；但又不能忘记。</p>\n<p>沉沉浮浮中，记忆如同一条长线。忘记了一天，第二天还会想起那熟悉的一切一切。</p>\n<p>原来这才是对自己最大的挑战；我笑自己。</p>\n<p>我倒退，你却紧跟着追上来。我竟然没有计划好没有你的明天将会是什么样子的。</p>\n<p>日复一日，我沿着那条熟悉的小路。想要更勇敢一点，再一点。</p>\n<p>我只是想做一个朴实的女孩子；简简单单就好。</p>\n<p>却它不同意；让我重复这别人的路。</p>\n<p>我写起了日记。记录每一天的事情，试图用它们填满我的生活。生活总是要等待的，等待那些你未发现的幸福。</p>\n<p>还记得曾经我们一起放风筝的样子，天空是蓝色的，清新的味道钻入我的鼻子。我肆无忌惮的光着脚奔跑，看风筝放飞，很自由的样子，殊不知，却总有一线牵挂。</p>\n<p>有一天我长大了；有一天我不在幼稚了；有一天我做回了我真正的自己了；有一天我们都离开了。</p>\n<p>有一天我不在写日记了。因为那天，拉起了旅行箱，决定去旅行散心。</p>\n<p>旅行中，好像也长大了许多。对当初的选择也有些后悔，但是却来不及挽留在沙漏里溜掉的时光。</p>\n<p>或许我着急赶回去，因为我要去把握住我的幸福，不容错过。</p>\n<p>或许幸福，就在远处等着，从未走远。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqp