tent/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript><a href=\'http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/8C661306-09FC-42BF-A48B-E672359F19A5.jpg\' title=\'8C661306-09FC-42BF-A48B-E672359F19A5\'><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/8C661306-09FC-42BF-A48B-E672359F19A5-190x256.jpg\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"8C661306-09FC-42BF-A48B-E672359F19A5\" /><noscript><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/8C661306-09FC-42BF-A48B-E672359F19A5-190x256.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"8C661306-09FC-42BF-A48B-E672359F19A5\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1714),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>曾经牵手的指尖，在夜里独自合十。风吹沙吹成沙漠，你等我，等成十年漫长的打坐。我寻你，花掉一整幅青春，岁月如歌。<br />\n<span id=\"more-236020\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1691.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1691.jpg\" alt=\"1691\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236021\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1691.jpg\" alt=\"1691\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236021\" /></noscript></a><br />\n远离人生的抱怨，做人生的智者！远离抱怨的世界，学会感恩。你会感受到爱的涌动，温暖的气息遍布周围的世界，从而收获一道世间最美的风景。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1695.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1695.jpg\" alt=\"1695\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236022\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/1695.jpg\" alt=\"1695\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236022\" /></noscript></a><br />\n都見不著、摸不到。而如今我更加怕死，怕我死了之後，妳在這個世上將會說不出的孤單寂寞。怕死了以后没有人能象我这样的关怀你,叫你盖好被子，注意身体，早上记得吃早饭，怕没有人能逗你开心，逗你笑。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/91.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/91.jpg\" alt=\"91\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236023\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/91.jpg\" alt=\"91\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236023\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我一个人在茫茫人海中真的已经很疲惫了，希望你的出现能够帮我一起分担，无论是快乐或是悲伤，好吗？自从和你在一起 你之后，我的灵魂好像被你摄去了一般，你的影子，占据了我每一个记忆。你能理解我的痴心吗？这一生我只牵你的手，因为今生有你早已足够。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/92.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/92.jpg\" alt=\"92\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236024\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/92.jpg\" alt=\"92\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236024\" /></noscript></a><br />\n轻轻地爱你，让爱恋滋润你的心房；轻轻的想你，让思念充满我的内心；轻轻的感觉你，让温柔吹拂我的心灵；轻轻地爱你，直到永远。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/93.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/93.jpg\" alt=\"93\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236025\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/93.jpg\" alt=\"93\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236025\" /></noscript></a><br />\n雨打在我脸上，洗刷着你的耳语，风卷走了雨伞，卷走残存的痕迹，心依然在街上，反复地走来走去，爱已经被放逐，伸出双手握不住你，想你的夜晚没有你，这一种感觉太熟悉，想你的夜晚没有你，只有，一往情深的自己。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/94.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/94.jpg\" alt=\"94\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236026\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/94.jpg\" alt=\"94\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236026\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我不知道我的生命有多长，所以，我每天都会告诉自己，我这一生中最在乎的是你！！！因为有了你才让我感觉到世上的温暖，你在的时候，你是一切；你不在的时候，一切是你！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/95.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/95.jpg\" alt=\"95\" width=\"335\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236027\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/95.jpg\" alt=\"95\" width=\"335\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236027\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人生，只有一次，所以我们要倍加珍惜。为使人生更加美好，就要像雄鹰那样勇敢地飞翔，即便遇到狂风 暴雨，亦或惊涛骇浪，人生也不失幸福与美好。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/98.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/98.jpg\" alt=\"98\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236028\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/98.jpg\" alt=\"98\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236028\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我从不知道什么是幸福，直到有一天我认识了你。我才明白了。如果你要问我为什么爱你，我有一百个理由来回答，最关键的一点就是因为我爱你所以爱你。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/99.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/99.jpg\" alt=\"99\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236029\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/99.jpg\" alt=\"99\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236029\" /></noscript></a><br />\n也许某天，在喧闹的城市中，你我擦肩而过。我会停住脚步，凝望远去的背影，告诉自己：那个人我曾经爱过！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/100.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/100.jpg\" alt=\"100\" width=\"500\" height=\"384\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236030\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/100.jpg\" alt=\"100\" width=\"500\" height=\"384\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236030\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1715),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>时光在光与影的交错中总会显得凌乱无比，季节被切割成碎片牵连出一系列与旁人有共鸣的片段。有和风有草坪有泥土味道有零碎阳光。少年的天空有五颜六色的光怪陆离。<br />\n<span id=\"more-236047\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21311.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21311.jpg\" alt=\"2131\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236059\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21311.jpg\" alt=\"2131\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236059\" /></noscript></a><br />\n安静就好，何必自寻烦恼。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21321.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21321.jpg\" alt=\"2132\" width=\"490\" height=\"319\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236060\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21321.jpg\" alt=\"2132\" width=\"490\" height=\"319\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236060\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生活的真谛在于宽恕与忘记。宽恕那些值得的人，忘记那些不值得的人。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21331.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21331.jpg\" alt=\"2133\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236061\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21331.jpg\" alt=\"2133\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236061\" /></noscript></a><br />\n倘若心中愿意，道路千千条。倘若心中不愿意，理由万万个。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21341.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21341.jpg\" alt=\"2134\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236062\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21341.jpg\" alt=\"2134\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236062\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一件心事，想开了，固然很好。一件心事，怎么想也想不开，干脆将它丢掉。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21351.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21351.jpg\" alt=\"2135\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236063\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21351.jpg\" alt=\"2135\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236063\" /></noscript></a><br />\n其实，朋友也许就是这个样子：未必要什么天长地久，也未必时时见面联系。在一些时候，可以彼此温暖，彼此慰藉，彼此鼓舞，那就足够。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21361.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21361.jpg\" alt=\"2136\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236064\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21361.jpg\" alt=\"2136\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236064\" /></noscript></a><br />\n活着需要一点耐心，活得久，才能站在山头，欣赏自己走过的崎岖山路。人的困境可能会持续很久，我所能做的最好的事情，就是找些事做，然后等待转机。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21371.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21371.jpg\" alt=\"2137\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236065\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21371.jpg\" alt=\"2137\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236065\" /></noscript></a><br />\n世上最糟糕的感受，就是不得不怀疑先前深信不疑的东西。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21381.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21381.jpg\" alt=\"2138\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236066\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21381.jpg\" alt=\"2138\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236066\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人生，都有“艰难”这个副产品，却也有时间这副良药，将不幸变成有幸，是生活给我们最好的礼物。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21391.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21391.jpg\" alt=\"2139\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236067\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21391.jpg\" alt=\"2139\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236067\" /></noscript></a><br />\n平庸的人，只是眷念近处的风景，贪恋凡俗的奢华，最终忘了赶路，舒适并安逸着，且自鸣得意，终一无所成；优秀的人，独行在沉默的时光中，忍受着清平与寂寞，从不哀怨，从不言苦，踏着血汗的阶梯，攀上了他人企盼的高度。曾经的苦与累，不是为别人受的，那是你蛰伏的背景，回眸的闪光。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21401.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21401.jpg\" alt=\"2140\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236068\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/21401.jpg\" alt=\"2140\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236068\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1716),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>旧日的时光，就如一滴水流进了大海，早已不见踪影，连同记忆里人，留下的仅仅是些许淡漠的回忆。你若赐我一段浮华，我便许你满世繁花。<br />\n<span id=\"more-235994\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2481.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2481.jpg\" alt=\"2481\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235995\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2481.jpg\" alt=\"2481\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235995\" /></noscript></a><br />\n只有在你最落魄时，才会知道谁是为你担心的笨蛋，谁是形同陌路的混蛋。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2482.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2482.jpg\" alt=\"2482\" width=\"500\" height=\"359\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235996\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2482.jpg\" alt=\"2482\" width=\"500\" height=\"359\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235996\" /></noscript></a><br />\n所谓幸福，是有一颗感恩的心，一个健康的身体，一份称心的工作，一位深爱你的爱人，一帮值得信赖的朋友。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2483.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2483.jpg\" alt=\"2483\" width=\"494\" height=\"328\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235997\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2483.jpg\" alt=\"2483\" width=\"494\" height=\"328\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235997\" /></noscript></a><br />\n理想就是当你想它时，你是快乐的；欲望就是当你想它时，你是痛苦的。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2484.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2484.jpg\" alt=\"2484\" width=\"500\" height=\"624\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235998\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2484.jpg\" alt=\"2484\" width=\"500\" height=\"624\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235998\" /></noscript></a><br />\n有些人不会忘，由于不舍得；有些人必需要忘，因为不值得。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2485.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2485.jpg\" alt=\"2485\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235999\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2485.jpg\" alt=\"2485\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235999\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果做出的每一个选择，都怕将来自己后悔。那么，要青春做什么？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2486.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2486.jpg\" alt=\"2486\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236000\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2486.jpg\" alt=\"2486\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236000\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人生就是一场旅行，不在乎目的地，在乎的应该是沿途的风景以及看风景的心情。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2487.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2487.jpg\" alt=\"2487\" width=\"499\" height=\"373\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236001\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2487.jpg\" alt=\"2487\" width=\"499\" height=\"373\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236001\" /></noscript></a><br />\n朋友是我们为自己挑选的家人。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2488.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2488.jpg\" alt=\"2488\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236002\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2488.jpg\" alt=\"2488\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236002\" /></noscript></a><br />\n青春是一场无知的奔忙，总会留下颠沛流离的伤。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2489.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2489.jpg\" alt=\"2489\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236003\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2489.jpg\" alt=\"2489\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236003\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生命中，有一个人可以去惦念，是缘分；有一个人可以惦念自己，是幸福。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2490.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2490.jpg\" alt=\"2490\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-236004\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2490.jpg\" alt=\"2490\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-236004\" /></noscript></a><br />\n请别伤我的心，那里面住的是你。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1717),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>有时候，我觉得自己很傻<br />\n因为喜欢的人是你，所以觉得自己真的好傻<br />\n明明没有可能，明明没有机会<br />\n我自己也很清楚这是一场没有结果的事情<br />\n但是，还是会时不时地想起你<br />\n然后，心就莫名地痛了<br />\n<span id=\"more-235940\"></span><br />\n有时候，有些话<br />\n说的人不会在意，但是听的人却用心记住了<br />\n用心记住的人好傻，就像我一样<br />\n说着无心，听者有意<br />\n这句话，在若干年后，居然在我身上验证了</p>\n<p>这也许就是一场惩罚<br />\n高考结束后<br />\n是我人生中一段最黑暗的日子<br />\n所有的委屈，所有的痛苦，一切的一切<br />\n当我发现自己不能再继续承受的时候<br />\n就这样<br />\n突然的爆发了</p>\n<p>所以<br />\n曾经在外人眼里坚不可摧/阳光无敌/活泼开朗的我<br />\n也会选择每天躲在一个角落里<br />\n沉默不语/黯然神伤<br />\n觉得全世界都在与我为敌<br />\n是的<br />\n只有我心里才知道我是多么的不甘</p>\n<p>这样的我<br />\n没了曾经坚硬的保护甲<br />\n只能露出最脆弱的一面<br />\n所以<br />\n连我也不知道<br />\n你为什么就这样突然闯进</p>\n<p>如果是原先的我<br />\n那么我们就只能是两条平行线<br />\n但是就算是唯一的交集过后<br />\n还是改变了轨迹<br />\n却留我在原地返回不了我自己的轨道 </p>\n<p>我不喜欢悲剧<br />\n更反感说散就散了的结局<br />\n所以转身陌路<br />\n对于我们来说，才是最好的结局吧<br />\n只当是一场梦</p>\n<p>有些事情，可能没有人能知道了<br />\n那又怎样<br />\n就让它消失在时间里吧<br />\n化作青烟，再也遍寻不到<br />\n也没有人再会回忆起</p>\n<p>其实我真的很想对你说<br />\n我没有骗过你<br />\n我是真的喜欢你<br />\n我知道你不喜欢我<br />\n我也不期望会在一起</p>\n<p>所以<br />\n有些事情，还是不要说出口吧<br />\n散了就散了<br />\n所有的都遗忘吧<br />\n随我高考后的那个夏天一起消失吧<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.co