的温习着自我温暖。其实爱情，并不像我们想的那样纯粹。所以，难免也责怪青春的手，把相爱写成了相爱过。</p>\n<p>送一首歌给你吧。梁静茹的《可惜不是你》。</p>\n<h6>{花开左岸，葬于右岸}</h6>\n<p>很久很久以前，你来到这里。看到一个女孩一个人在这个世界，写着忧伤的文字，孤寂。你说，你要快乐起来。你要相信，终有一天繁花会开满这个世界。 </p>\n<p>很久很久以后，你回到这里。看到满地繁华，热闹欢腾。 你什么都不说。只是静静的在打着酱油，静默无语。我说，原本的‘一花一世界’已经失去了最初的定义。再繁华又有何意？ </p>\n<p>当初只是：想，在一地凋零里拾起刹那的芳华；想，于苍白凄冷里找寻片刻的温暖。如今却惟见，纠缠不清的往昔，破碎在掌心。 看，那些流逝在花开花落的刹那，被岁月婉转于梦起梦落的片刻。我想，久久的颠沛流离后，这一场烟火般绚烂的繁华终会止于岁月的静静湖水中，波澜不再。 </p>\n<p>如今，岁月静好。这里依然是安静的一花一世界。可惜你，只是我唯剩的残念。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/