ata-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2810.jpg\" alt=\"2810\" width=\"500\" height=\"293\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235717\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/2810.jpg\" alt=\"2810\" width=\"500\" height=\"293\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235717\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1723),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>Todd Laffler在十几岁时开始了摄影生涯，他的母亲教会他如何拍摄和冲印黑白照片。拍摄滑板让他拥有了寻找和拍摄最佳时刻的第六感，因此在拍摄婚礼现场时，他善于捕捉关键时刻的情感，并展现出了极好的摄影技巧。<br />\n<span id=\"more-235693\"></span><br />\nTodd Laffler表示，“对客户来说，最重要的是艺术的呈现和人们之间的共通关系，而不仅仅是时间的复制。客户希望他们的摄影师更具有亲和力和人情味。”</p>\n<p>当拍摄婚礼的时候，Todd Laffler会选择在比较轻松和悠闲的氛围中把握自然的场景。做安静的观察者和独立的拍摄者，随时把握和捕捉正在进行的事物。Todd</p>\n<p>Laffler认为婚礼上拍出的照片应该是独一无二的，充满艺术的故事<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/951.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/951.jpg\" alt=\"951\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235694\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/951.jpg\" alt=\"951\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235694\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/952.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/952.jpg\" alt=\"952\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235695\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/952.jpg\" alt=\"952\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235695\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/953.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/953.jpg\" alt=\"953\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235696\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/953.jpg\" alt=\"953\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235696\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/954.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/954.jpg\" alt=\"954\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235697\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/954.jpg\" alt=\"954\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235697\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/955.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/955.jpg\" alt=\"955\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235698\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/955.jpg\" alt=\"955\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235698\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/956.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/956.jpg\" alt=\"956\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235699\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/956.jpg\" alt=\"956\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235699\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/957.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/957.jpg\" alt=\"957\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235700\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/957.jpg\" alt=\"957\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235700\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/958.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/958.jpg\" alt=\"958\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235701\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/958.jpg\" alt=\"958\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235701\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/959.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/959.jpg\" alt=\"959\" width=\"500\" height=\"250\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235702\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/959.jpg\" alt=\"959\" width=\"500\" height=\"250\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235702\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/960.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/960.jpg\" alt=\"960\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235703\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/960.jpg\" alt=\"960\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235703\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1724),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>其实想说很多，可是忘了说什么。<br />\n有时会觉得自己在和自己说假话，比如嘴上说不害怕，其实害怕得要命，怀疑存在的瞬间，如此这般这般。<br />\n <span id=\"more-235594\"></span><br />\n我有最美好的二十岁，肆无忌惮去臭美，改变风格，拿手机镜头框下一个又一个大笑亦或搞怪的瞬间。爱自己，凭什么不要记住美丽。我依赖父母，沉浸且享受这种家长与孩子间的关怀。不同于年少厌恶他们的说教，死命想要逃离，开始觉得只有他们的唠叨才是爱得最温暖。可是，可是，不得不冒出这个念头：二十岁再不独立，感觉自己就真的残废了。</p>\n<p>在不习惯里找习惯，在陌生的境遇里找归属感，否定自己的不成熟，却迟迟不得出路。不想委屈求全，下决心不能服软，然而一次又一次妥协，循环往复。<br />\n来这个地方上学，已经第三年，每每有人不经意问起你哪儿人，不假思索，随口说出这里的名字，心里都会卡一下，仿佛说过的话早已漏洞百出，原来潜意识里就认定，我从来就不属于这里。</p>\n<p>这里的天气到了秋天的时候就会以加速的趋势开始交替，秋天好似四季里的过客，瞅一眼就离开。不久之后来临的是干白冷冷的冬季，还好还好，早就有心理准备，冬天啊冬天，迈开步子，你来吧。</p>\n<p>其实，我也是有改变的吧。。。。。。</p>\n<p>一个人在这里重新适应早就走过六年的群居生活，诸多不如意堆叠一起，多了也就没了感觉。如果真有机会，我倒是真想遇见那年十五六岁的自己，笑着问她，喜不喜欢现在的我。</p>\n<p>没有恋爱，不是因为单着久了就习惯一个人，因为年纪在那里，也不是不愿意拥有，大概还是因为初衷，我要寻着一个契机，在一个对的时间获得一个彼此对的人。倘若回去那个年纪，我会执拗地认定一个人，原因是我喜欢。而现在，和大多数人一样，会考虑他是否足够认真，足够努力，是否真的有能力就和自己这样慢慢走下去。</p>\n<p>三年啊，长了很长的头发，这应该是时光最直接的见证。三三同学，记得努力。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fq