p-content/uploads/2013/09/11110-300x295.jpg\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden attachment-onehalfsquare-inpost\" alt=\"111\" /><noscript><img width=\"300\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11110-300x295.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onehalfsquare-inpost\" alt=\"111\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1731),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>这一年，我懂得了日久不一定生情，但一定能够见人心。<br />\n<span id=\"more-235237\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/6.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/6.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235238\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/6.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235238\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得了原来讨厌的可以依旧讨厌，喜欢的却有很多可以不再喜欢。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4101.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4101.jpg\" alt=\"4101\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235239\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4101.jpg\" alt=\"4101\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235239\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得没有谁会像父母一样一直包容并原谅你。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4102.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4102.jpg\" alt=\"4102\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235240\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4102.jpg\" alt=\"4102\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235240\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得了生容易，活容易，生活不容易。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4103.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4103.jpg\" alt=\"4103\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235241\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4103.jpg\" alt=\"4103\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235241\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得了好多人不喜欢你，却还会对你笑。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4104.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4104.jpg\" alt=\"4104\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235242\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4104.jpg\" alt=\"4104\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235242\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得了好多时候两个人走近是为了相互取暖。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4105.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4105.jpg\" alt=\"4105\" width=\"500\" height=\"359\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235243\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4105.jpg\" alt=\"4105\" width=\"500\" height=\"359\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235243\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得了老师可以淡定到即使全班都不听课也可以讲个涛涛不绝。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4106.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4106.jpg\" alt=\"4106\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235244\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4106.jpg\" alt=\"4106\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235244\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得了女生多的地方真的很烦人，即使你什么都不争也会被算计，想要安静根本不太可能。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4107.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4107.jpg\" alt=\"4107\" width=\"500\" height=\"307\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235245\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4107.jpg\" alt=\"4107\" width=\"500\" height=\"307\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235245\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我懂得了有得人真的可以为了蝇头微利去出卖自己的灵魂和一切。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4108.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4108.jpg\" alt=\"4108\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235246\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4108.jpg\" alt=\"4108\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235246\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我怕了，因为容忍往往被有些人看作是软弱。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4109.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4109.jpg\" alt=\"4109\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235247\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4109.jpg\" alt=\"4109\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235247\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这一年，我怕了，因为没有永恒的朋友只有永恒的利益，原来是真的。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1732),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>现在的生活并不是我想要的，但确实是我自找的，所以活该，我认了。<br />\n<span id=\"more-235224\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11011.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11011.jpg\" alt=\"1101\" width=\"500\" height=\"380\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235225\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11011.jpg\" alt=\"1101\" width=\"500\" height=\"380\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235225\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11021.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11021.jpg\" alt=\"1102\" width=\"468\" height=\"367\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235226\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11021.jpg\" alt=\"1102\" width=\"468\" height=\"367\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235226\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11031.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11031.jpg\" alt=\"1103\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235227\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11031.jpg\" alt=\"1103\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235227\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11041.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11041.jpg\" alt=\"1104\" width=\"468\" height=\"424\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235228\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11041.jpg\" alt=\"1104\" width=\"468\" height=\"424\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235228\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11051.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11051.jpg\" alt=\"1105\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235229\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11051.jpg\" alt=\"1105\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235229\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11061.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11061.jpg\" alt=\"1106\" width=\"468\" height=\"389\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235230\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11061.jpg\" alt=\"1106\" width=\"468\" height=\"389\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235230\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11071.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11071.jpg\" alt=\"1107\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235231\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11071.jpg\" alt=\"1107\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235231\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11081.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11081.jpg\" alt=\"1108\" width=\"500\" height=\"661\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235232\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11081.jpg\" alt=\"1108\" width=\"500\" height=\"661\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235232\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11091.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11091.jpg\" alt=\"1109\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235233\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11091.jpg\" alt=\"1109\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235233\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11101.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11101.jpg\" alt=\"1110\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-235234\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11101.jpg\" alt=\"1110\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235234\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1733),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>青春，沿着一朵花开的轨迹，从含苞等待开放，再从待放刹那盛开，接着由怒放接近凋零，最后色褪入土。<br />\n碎片，掩盖一世沧桑的落寞，将树轮一圈一圈刻画，将银杏叶一片一片染黄，将聚合一年一年推迟，将所有完整一块一块分割。<br />\n<span id=\"more-235150\"></span><br />\n青春是一切美好的堆积。阳光，是澄清到透明的温暖。蓝天，是澄澈到深邃的宁静。偶有伤感，也会悄悄寻找着午后的暖意。每次在慵懒的午后，看到丝丝亮亮的暖光，都会期待着奇迹的发生——相信这个世界任何事情都会有转机, 相信命运的宽厚和美好。<br />\n碎片是一切美好的落寞。乌云，是灰暗到黑霾的阴郁。暴风，是猛烈到撕扯的刺痛。偶有迷失，也会默默守候着孤单的心事。古典爱情故事中，失散多年的夫妻在人约黄昏的七夕夜破镜重圆是温存的美好。人生几何，譬如朝露，羡慕而已。<br />\n原谅我——是骚情的人。（【骚情】大唐标准语言陕西话，略带贬义，情感泛滥。）<br />\n原谅我——有些东西，被岁月渲染，虽不曾拥有，却像烙铁打了印一般，深入骨髓，刺痛神经。<br />\n理性是大多数正常的人，或是在“念念不忘中，遗忘某些过往”，或是在“不曾拥有，不会伤感”的理念下释怀。而我，感性作祟，只能在屡试屡败后，承认世间的无奈，有一种，叫做——想，但做不到。<br />\n想念在特定条件下是甜蜜的，而另外些是苦涩的。我也说不清是什么作祟，总觉得只有在凉凉的深秋夜，写下这些文字，才能彻底断了我对那些旧时光的深深地怀念。<br />\n我不能将过去的一切，赘述在这里，因为自私地想让它们只属于我的过了的时光。但是，我已长大，要学会离别，学会淡然。当我抛弃你们的时候，有深深地不舍。可是就像每一首骊歌都有的那种表达——长亭外，古道边，一朝芳草碧连天。<br />\n我还很单纯，相信未来，我们会在世界的屋脊相遇！那时，我们相互对视，静静地，呼吸藏着浪漫的空气，美好到无可救药。<br />\n而此刻，为了成长。只是再见，青春。只能再见，碎片。<br />\n再见，是为了某一天的再次遇见。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http: