-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3301.jpg\" alt=\"3301\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234612\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3301.jpg\" alt=\"3301\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234612\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3302.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3302.jpg\" alt=\"3302\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234613\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3302.jpg\" alt=\"3302\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234613\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3303.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3303.jpg\" alt=\"3303\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234614\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3303.jpg\" alt=\"3303\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234614\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3304.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3304.jpg\" alt=\"3304\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234615\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3304.jpg\" alt=\"3304\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234615\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3305.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3305.jpg\" alt=\"3305\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234616\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3305.jpg\" alt=\"3305\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234616\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3306.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3306.jpg\" alt=\"3306\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234617\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3306.jpg\" alt=\"3306\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234617\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3307.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3307.jpg\" alt=\"3307\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234618\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3307.jpg\" alt=\"3307\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234618\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3308.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3308.jpg\" alt=\"3308\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234619\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3308.jpg\" alt=\"3308\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234619\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3309.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3309.jpg\" alt=\"3309\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234620\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3309.jpg\" alt=\"3309\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234620\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3310.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3310.jpg\" alt=\"3310\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234621\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3310.jpg\" alt=\"3310\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234621\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1744),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>【关于你】兜兜转转，不兜不转，我们终于，还是在爱里失散了。你从来不说喜欢，却一直说着似有似无的许诺。我是傻的，也是自恋的，于是一直自以为你是喜欢我的。2013年的中秋，等到月圆之夜，也没有等到你的电话，甚至是扣扣上一句“中秋快乐”。<br />\n<span id=\"more-234812\"></span><br />\n那么那些自己做过的傻事，你应该不曾对我做过。不会上扣扣只是为了看你在不在线，不会经常想念，不会关注签名变化，不会在没有人的时候偷偷看着聊天记录一个人傻傻地笑，总之，不会想要亲口对我说“我喜欢你”。一个人想了很多，终于下定决心放弃。好吧，我承认我是绝望了。也许这种绝望早已在不知不自觉中慢慢积累发芽，但至少在今天凌晨的那一刻，那么清晰地感受到了痛楚。至于那些无处安放的回忆，犹豫了很久，选择了最简单最直接的方式——D-E-L-E-T-E。你送我的桃花，我会一直戴着，去远行，然后忘记你。<br />\n【关于远行】一直在担心钱不够花要去的地方不好玩还没有充分的准备这些杂七杂八的问题，可是今天突然就想通了。钱用完的时候，就是逼着自己去挣钱的时候。至于要去的地方到底值不值得去，我相信不管去哪里，出去一趟，总会有不一样的收获。想走的时候就出发吧。<br />\n【关于学习】如果没有其他特别优秀的地方，那就做一个学霸吧。说好的去图书馆自习室看书写作业学摄影改掉拖延症都要慢慢实现。<br />\n深更半夜，改了扣扣昵称、签名、个人说明。不是形式主义，是跟旧时光说再见的一种方式。做一个自己喜欢的自己，加油。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/im