 alt=\"18-3\" /><noscript><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18-3-190x256.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"18-3\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1745),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>在这个浮华到坚硬的年代，还是回到心中的那个故乡吧！慢三拍，静一生，一间小店，足矣。<br />\n<span id=\"more-234639\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10911.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10911.jpg\" alt=\"1091\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234640\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10911.jpg\" alt=\"1091\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234640\" /></noscript></a><br />\n让你难过的事情，有一天，你一定会笑着说出来。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10921.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10921.jpg\" alt=\"1092\" width=\"500\" height=\"355\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234641\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10921.jpg\" alt=\"1092\" width=\"500\" height=\"355\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234641\" /></noscript></a><br />\n朋友之间不言谢，遇见，就是幸福。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10931.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10931.jpg\" alt=\"1093\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234642\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10931.jpg\" alt=\"1093\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234642\" /></noscript></a><br />\n你的负担将变成礼物，你受的苦将照亮你的路。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10941.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10941.jpg\" alt=\"1094\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234643\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10941.jpg\" alt=\"1094\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234643\" /></noscript></a><br />\n有一天你会明白，善良比聪明更难。聪明是一种天赋，而善良是一种选择。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10951.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10951.jpg\" alt=\"1095\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234644\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10951.jpg\" alt=\"1095\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234644\" /></noscript></a><br />\n青春是一场大雨，即使感冒了，还盼回头再淋一次。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10961.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10961.jpg\" alt=\"1096\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234645\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10961.jpg\" alt=\"1096\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234645\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我以为只要很认真的喜欢就能打动一个人，到后来，却只打动了我自己。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10971.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10971.jpg\" alt=\"1097\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234646\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10971.jpg\" alt=\"1097\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234646\" /></noscript></a><br />\n最好的感觉，是有人懂你的欲言又止。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10981.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10981.jpg\" alt=\"1098\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234647\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10981.jpg\" alt=\"1098\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234647\" /></noscript></a><br />\n不要着急，最好的总会在最不经意的时候出现。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10991.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10991.jpg\" alt=\"1099\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234648\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10991.jpg\" alt=\"1099\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234648\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人生是场荒芜的旅行，冷暖自知，苦乐在心。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11001.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11001.jpg\" alt=\"1100\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234649\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11001.jpg\" alt=\"1100\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234649\" /></noscript></a><br />\n选一种姿态，让自己活得无可替代。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1746),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>幕色的光亮下<br />\n耀出那如针细的裂缝<br />\n情人的眼泪汇入<br />\n化成无骨的丝<br />\n也就是如此<br />\n情人的眼泪<br />\n成了浇灌铁树的养料<br />\n它就这样的开了花<br />\n<span id=\"more-234476\"></span><br />\n心灵的荒野<br />\n在大白天的日子下<br />\n炫耀着胸膛里那颗火红的心<br />\n在被光亮照耀后<br />\n散发出一股奇特的香<br />\n就像是情人的眼泪<br />\n诉说心里的苦惆<br />\n那是一种凄风苦雨</p>\n<p>一场雨过后<br />\n洗净了那被暗灰色遮蔽的眼<br />\n褪祛了那层尘埃<br />\n原来这场雨是情人的眼泪<br />\n把虚偟拉回了现实<br />\n其实有那么一种介质<br />\n从有到无而又消失<br />\n摸不透猜不着</p>\n<p>那是<br />\n情人的眼泪<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_fli