www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3319.jpg\" alt=\"3319\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234448\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3319.jpg\" alt=\"3319\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234448\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3311.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3311.jpg\" alt=\"3311\" width=\"468\" height=\"389\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234440\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3311.jpg\" alt=\"3311\" width=\"468\" height=\"389\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234440\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3318.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3318.jpg\" alt=\"3318\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234447\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3318.jpg\" alt=\"3318\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234447\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3317.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3317.jpg\" alt=\"3317\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234446\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3317.jpg\" alt=\"3317\" width=\"468\" height=\"378\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234446\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3316.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3316.jpg\" alt=\"3316\" width=\"468\" height=\"389\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234445\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3316.jpg\" alt=\"3316\" width=\"468\" height=\"389\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234445\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1748),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>蓦然回首，曾经沧海桑田，已是物是人非。回忆却依然夸饰着伤感。若遗憾可以如昨日黄花，随着厚厚的霜色而枯萎凋凌。我又何须缅怀于过去。<br />\n<span id=\"more-234373\"></span><br />\n人生若只如初见，何事西风悲画扇。</p>\n<p>是啊，如若只如初见，那该有多好。各自转身，就能两两相忘。那么就无须感伤于离别。那比翼连枝的幸福已成往日的追忆，只剩下一身的惆然。望眼昨日消失于茫茫红尘，可否就让曾经的美丽在飞逝的时光中瞬灭？<br />\n昨日已被今天处死，我却还怀念些什么？</p>\n<p>叹一句当时只道是寻常。</p>\n<p>谁珍惜过当时的美丽？谁又能忘却曾经的情意？沧海桑田最终还是禁不起时光的蹉跎，不再地久天长了。<br />\n虽然时间可以淡，却不能忘。不断相交替换的回忆影象，就犹如发生在昨天。纵然往事已成空，回忆却依然夸饰着遗憾，翻滚着不停歇。</p>\n<p>爱过，错过，泪过，痛过，只剩淡淡残念，深埋心底。也许多年后，每每想起，会有那一点遗憾，但这残缺不全的美丽，却使生命蒙上了一道惘然的美丽。</p>\n<p>想回到过去，回到那初见之时。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy 