忘不了谁的 有的只是愿不愿忘记</p>\n<p>开始的开始我觉得我的生命里再也不会有那种温暖岁月的人</p>\n<p>可是后来我发现没有谁是离不开谁的</p>\n<p>你都如何回忆我 带着微笑或是沉默</p>\n<p>说不出为什么有你在的时候 就是安定的理所当然</p>\n<p>我希望若干年后我能在人潮汹涌的大街一眼就认出你</p>\n<p>我希望那时的你微笑依然如初</p>\n<p>我不知道以后站在你身边的会是谁</p>\n<p>我不知道我会不会在我不在的时候你会发疯似的找我</p>\n<p>不过你身边的她一定会很幸福</p>\n<p>我觉得的时光就像是一组老照片</p>\n<p>它清晰的样子逐渐模糊 等到我们都忘记的时候</p>\n<p>它就像海藻一般缠绕在每一个深夜</p>\n<p>如果回到过去 我不愿物是人非 只愿你依然会记得我<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"la