tp://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/361.jpg\" alt=\"361\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234260\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/361.jpg\" alt=\"361\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234260\" /></noscript></a><br />\n往往最在乎的、最在意的、到嘴边就成“无所谓”了。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/362.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/362.jpg\" alt=\"362\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234261\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/362.jpg\" alt=\"362\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234261\" /></noscript></a><br />\n只要人生不止，就寂寞不已。寂寞人生爱无休，寂寞是爱永远的主题。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/363.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/363.jpg\" alt=\"363\" width=\"500\" height=\"740\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234262\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/363.jpg\" alt=\"363\" width=\"500\" height=\"740\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234262\" /></noscript></a><br />\n顺其自然，不代表我们可以不努力，而是努力之后有勇气接受成败。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/364.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/364.jpg\" alt=\"364\" width=\"500\" height=\"451\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234263\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/364.jpg\" alt=\"364\" width=\"500\" height=\"451\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234263\" /></noscript></a><br />\n曾听人说过，回忆是一座桥，却是通向那寂寞的牢。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/365.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/365.jpg\" alt=\"365\" width=\"424\" height=\"640\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234264\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/365.jpg\" alt=\"365\" width=\"424\" height=\"640\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234264\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生活就像是彩虹，你既需要阳光，也需要雨水才能画出绚烂的颜色。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/366.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/366.jpg\" alt=\"366\" width=\"433\" height=\"640\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234265\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/366.jpg\" alt=\"366\" width=\"433\" height=\"640\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234265\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人越往上走，心应该越能往下沉，心里踏实了之后，脚下的路才走得安稳。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/367.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/367.jpg\" alt=\"367\" width=\"427\" height=\"640\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234266\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/367.jpg\" alt=\"367\" width=\"427\" height=\"640\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234266\" /></noscript></a><br />\n在前行的路上，当你看到前方有你的身影时，别怕，那是你身后有阳光。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/368.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/368.jpg\" alt=\"368\" width=\"500\" height=\"746\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234267\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/368.jpg\" alt=\"368\" width=\"500\" height=\"746\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234267\" /></noscript></a><br />\n他爱你时，就算找不到一个理由也要和你在一起；他不爱你时，总会有千万个理由离开你。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/369.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/369.jpg\" alt=\"369\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234268\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/369.jpg\" alt=\"369\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234268\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一个能思想的人，才真是一个力量无边的人。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/370.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/370.jpg\" alt=\"370\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234269\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/370.jpg\" alt=\"370\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234269\" /></noscript></a><br />\n 初恋不一定能够成功，却是幸福的；婚姻是一种成功，却不一定幸福。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1752),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>回忆线条分明，思念转瞬云集，你们的身影在阳光与阴霾间屹立成一道风景。我悄悄躲在时光的暗影里，翻阅着一个人的苍凉悲伤。<br />\n<span id=\"more-234272\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1650.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1650.jpg\" alt=\"1650\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234273\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1650.jpg\" alt=\"1650\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234273\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1641.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1641.jpg\" alt=\"1641\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234274\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1641.jpg\" alt=\"1641\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234274\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1642.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1642.jpg\" alt=\"1642\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234275\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1642.jpg\" alt=\"1642\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234275\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1643.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1643.jpg\" alt=\"1643\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234276\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1643.jpg\" alt=\"1643\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234276\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1644.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1644.jpg\" alt=\"1644\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234277\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1644.jpg\" alt=\"1644\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234277\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1645.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1645.jpg\" alt=\"1645\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234278\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1645.jpg\" alt=\"1645\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234278\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1646.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1646.jpg\" alt=\"1646\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234279\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1646.jpg\" alt=\"1646\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234279\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1647.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1647.jpg\" alt=\"1647\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234280\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1647.jpg\" alt=\"1647\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234280\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1648.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1648.jpg\" alt=\"1648\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234281\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1648.jpg\" alt=\"1648\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234281\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1649.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1649.jpg\" alt=\"1649\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-234282\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1649.jpg\" alt=\"1649\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-234282\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1753),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>每一次日落，每一次捧着满身的金黄<br />\n每一次想象时间都是静止的意念<br />\n每一次静下来写根本不擅长的抒情<br />\n<span id=\"more-234212\"></span><br />\n最近的健忘症越来越严重，渴的时候倒了一杯开水，等到不渴时才发现原来我倒了一杯水。出门想买袋糖，结果买了一大袋不知道具体是什么的东西，回到家翻来覆去的找，就是没有想要的那袋糖。出门走了很远，突然想不起我到底有没有锁门，回忆了很久脑子里都没有我锁门的画面，最后还是打电话给邻居确认我到底是不是直接就出了门。</p>\n<p>一个人在雨天坐公交，把伞靠在旁边躲在最后一排，看着伞上的水迅速的浸湿周遭，觉得湿掉的灰尘黑黑的比飞舞的灰色丑很多，这话我是不是跟你说过，糟糕我又记不得了 </p>\n<p>如今的九月对于我而已已无往日的忙碌和煎熬<br />\n空虚乏味的生活显得无比的枯燥。</p>\n<p>那个低着头依旧掩不住笑意的女孩，此刻想到了谁<br />\n那个四处张望的小伙，寻找的是怎样一个身影<br />\n老人家满头的银发，是何时长出的第一根<br />\n小男孩的书包里，有没有装着零食<br />\n脚底打着节拍的他，耳机里，播放着怎样的歌曲<br />\n奔跑的中年男人，是要迟到了吗<br />\n那对甜蜜的情侣，有没有吵过架，会不会这样浓情到白头<br />\n买了那么多菜，肯定是丰盛的一餐，今天，对她而言，是一个怎样特别的日子<br />\n他人真的看着手机，会不会一抬头发现错过了班车<br />\n她肩上的纹身，有着一段怎样的故事<br />\n她脸上的雀斑，有没有让她自卑<br />\n婴儿车里纯真的小眼神 未来会有怎样理想<br />\n他一定是匆匆忙忙出的门，后脑上一撮头发很是傲娇<br />\n她的高跟鞋 那么高 ，被踩到会不会残废<br />\n……<br />\n车来了 ，他还在四处打量，他会去哪，谁在等他</p>\n<p>每天都有新的故事在发生，每天都有不一样的故事在上演。<br />\n王菲离婚了，大家又开始念叨不再相信爱情，<br />\n好像上次姚晨离婚的时候大家也这么说，后来的张柏芝也是这样。</p>\n<p>有人问我，能写出开心的文字，能带动他们一起开心么？<br />\n我想不出答案。<br />\n纵使我是开心的，这双手也写不出快乐。<br />\n如果说这是病，我也欣然接受。</p>\n<p>这个世界，依着轮回不灭的定律。<br />\n繁衍，消亡。幸福，惨淡。皆是早有注定。<br />\n我不信奉神灵，却也相信冥冥之中自由安排。<br />\n因此而心存敬畏。</p>\n<p>如果写不出，我就停笔。<br />\n这么想着也不是很难受。</p>\n<p>中午在跟小小树打电话，他跟我说了我从小长大的城市在发生着什么样的变化<br />\n我听着听着心里不知道是难过还是高兴<br />\n我熟悉的城市在我走后开始变得更美丽了，不知道我的那些小伙伴还是不是原来的你们<br />\n现在一直单曲循环李霄云的你看到的我是蓝色的<br />\n幻想年底回去站在那座城市里我会有怎样的感受<br />\n还能不能站在曾熟悉的地方遇见曾羁绊着我的人<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-cont