ent/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript><a href=\'http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/9370039598_a303d3d4e4_b.jpg\' title=\'9370039598_a303d3d4e4_b\'><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/9370039598_a303d3d4e4_b-190x256.jpg\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"9370039598_a303d3d4e4_b\" /><noscript><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/9370039598_a303d3d4e4_b-190x256.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"9370039598_a303d3d4e4_b\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1760),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>凡是你抗拒的，都会持续。因为当你抗拒某件事或情绪时，你会聚焦在那情绪或事上，这样就被赋予了更多能量，它就变得更强大了。负面情绪就像黑暗无法驱赶，唯一能做的，就是带进光来。喜悦是消融负面情绪最好的光。<br />\n<span id=\"more-233649\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1681.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1681.jpg\" alt=\"1681\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233650\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1681.jpg\" alt=\"1681\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233650\" /></noscript></a><br />\n或者成就了自己，或者成就了男人，对于女性来说，都叫幸福人生，当然最棒是两全。糟的是那些既不肯自强自立独立自主，又不甘愿成全家庭成就男人的女性……总一味抱怨他人给的不够或是自己遇人不淑，都是枉然。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1682.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1682.jpg\" alt=\"1682\" width=\"500\" height=\"696\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233651\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1682.jpg\" alt=\"1682\" width=\"500\" height=\"696\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233651\" /></noscript></a><br />\n所有敌对的开始就是一切悲剧的开始，不论任何事情，你在必须面对的时候所选择的态度其实就已经决定了整件事情的走向和结局。包容和接纳就会是祥和和喜剧，挑剔和敌对就一定是争吵和悲剧。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1683.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1683.jpg\" alt=\"1683\" width=\"500\" height=\"675\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233652\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1683.jpg\" alt=\"1683\" width=\"500\" height=\"675\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233652\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果有人在你最难过最美好最容易被辜负的时光里陪你走过那么一段，陪伴在你的身旁，那么无论将来那个人变成了什么样子，他还是不是你最好的朋友，你都没有办法割舍下，即便最后分开甚至陌生，也会对他心存感激。因为太多时候，交谈是一种莫大的温暖和美好。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1684.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1684.jpg\" alt=\"1684\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233653\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1684.jpg\" alt=\"1684\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233653\" /></noscript></a><br />\n任何值得你花时间要在一起的人，你都是在冒终究会失去的险，除非你会对失去紧张到让你去选择一个万无一失的人——某个对任何人都不可能有任何吸引力的人。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1685.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1685.jpg\" alt=\"1685\" width=\"450\" height=\"674\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233654\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1685.jpg\" alt=\"1685\" width=\"450\" height=\"674\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233654\" /></noscript></a><br />\n从一个不知所谓的女孩变成某人人生里的天降神兵。 把一个青涩害羞的男孩变成可以真正令你仰赖的大神。 其实我们缺乏的不是够好够对够靠谱的那个人，而是最后的最后，大家变成了彼此都需要的那一个人。如果你给他多一点时间，他也多给你一点时间，多好。 来，我们来谈一场不赶时间的恋爱。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1686.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1686.jpg\" alt=\"1686\" width=\"434\" height=\"640\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233655\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1686.jpg\" alt=\"1686\" width=\"434\" height=\"640\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233655\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我不再在太多人面前宣泄我的负面情绪。毋庸置疑，对于非常情绪化的我来说这是一个好现象，或许意味着我开始真正的理解何谓节制。生活中糟心的时刻依然还有，但我慢慢发觉，自己消化掉这些，所获得的经验和能量要比倾诉和抱怨强大得多。从前我依赖他人，如今我相信时间和我自己<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1687.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1687.jpg\" alt=\"1687\" width=\"500\" height=\"623\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233656\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1687.jpg\" alt=\"1687\" width=\"500\" height=\"623\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233656\" /></noscript></a><br />\n最傻的不是爱上不该爱的人，而是从来不做好为错误买单的准备。女人总有假装看不见时，但至少，当一切不得不面对的时候，你不是空有一副肉身去哭泣、去抵挡。越性情，越需有力量。女人的力量，不是为攻击，是为柔情和慈悲。没力量的女人，才怨恨，才残败，才无路可走。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1688.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1688.jpg\" alt=\"1688\" width=\"500\" height=\"744\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233657\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1688.jpg\" alt=\"1688\" width=\"500\" height=\"744\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233657\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一天里，清清醒醒思考的时间，其实少之又少。大部分人大部分时间，都是杂念纷飞，各种欲望 想像 回亿、无厘头想法，交叠呈现。所以，人若想变得聪明些，多练习专注，少胡思乱想 少胡言乱语，大概不消一阵子，別人就觉得你改变了。有时以为脑中空白一片，其实可能是昏沈 被一片杂念矇住了。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1689.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1689.jpg\" alt=\"1689\" width=\"432\" height=\"640\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233658\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1689.jpg\" alt=\"1689\" width=\"432\" height=\"640\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233658\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一个人越是诚实，保持诚实就越是容易，正如谎言说得越多，就越是要编造更多的谎言自圆其说。敢于面对事实的人，能够心胸坦荡地生活在天地间，也可借此摆脱良心的折磨和恐惧的威胁。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1690.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1690.jpg\" alt=\"1690\" width=\"500\" height=\"376\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233659\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1690.jpg\" alt=\"1690\" width=\"500\" height=\"376\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233659\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果我孤单一人，没有陪伴没有归属没有找到在这世上另一个自己，那么我会义无反顾的向前，去旅行去探求未知，主动出击，寻找，因为在这世上有些事总要去做，有些人总要去找。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1761),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>这个世界不是所有的人都懂你，被不懂的人误解无须争辩，我们选择沉默；有时被最爱的人误解，我们难过到不想争辩，也只有选择沈默。生命中往往有很多无言以对的时刻.不是所有的是非都能辩明，不是所有的纠葛都能理清，有时沉默就是我们最好的回答和诠释。<br />\n<span id=\"more-233612\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18611.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18611.jpg\" alt=\"1861\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233623\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18611.jpg\" alt=\"1861\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233623\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18621.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18621.jpg\" alt=\"1862\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233624\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18621.jpg\" alt=\"1862\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233624\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18631.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18631.jpg\" alt=\"1863\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233625\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.