\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233632\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1762),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>没有了夏日的烦燥<br />\n这样的夜显得安静也平静多了<br />\n一个人的街道<br />\n狭长而又古老<br />\n就这样<br />\n静静的走着想着<br />\n想着走着<br />\n只有心与心在默默的探讨<span id=\"more-233498\"></span><br />\n丝毫不受外界的干扰<br />\n偶尔有风不时地来凑凑热闹<br />\n伴随着树叶的欢笑<br />\n到处弥漫着静谧的味道<br />\n这个世界<br />\n霎那间<br />\n变得异常的奇妙<br />\n以至于我缓慢的步调<br />\n也不愿意来打乱这莫名的美好<br />\n然而<br />\n我的多情<br />\n却惹来了叶子的嘲笑<br />\n嘲笑是它们的<br />\n与你我无关<br />\n何必徒寻烦恼<br />\n一群人的街道<br />\n一个人的街道<br />\n我喜欢的只是热闹背后的思考<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.pn