7ns8a-300x300.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onehalfsquare-inpost\" alt=\"154847ql9kd5d68i47ns8a\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1766),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>多想喝一壶清淡的茶，不论暖和凉，品味半世的沧桑。多想写一封简洁的信，不留名和姓，寄去未知的天涯。多想爱一个平静的人，不问对与错，携手乱世的红尘。<br />\n<span id=\"more-233435\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3711.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3711.jpg\" alt=\"3711\" width=\"500\" height=\"339\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233436\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3711.jpg\" alt=\"3711\" width=\"500\" height=\"339\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233436\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生活虽然简单，但也没有你想象的那么简单。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3712.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3712.jpg\" alt=\"3712\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233437\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3712.jpg\" alt=\"3712\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233437\" /></noscript></a><br />\n坚持是一种可贵的品质，但是如果坚持了错的方向，那么勇于放下、改变也是一种智慧！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3713.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3713.jpg\" alt=\"3713\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233438\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3713.jpg\" alt=\"3713\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233438\" /></noscript></a><br />\n始终向上的力量，源自内心纯净的坚守。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3714.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3714.jpg\" alt=\"3714\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233439\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3714.jpg\" alt=\"3714\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233439\" /></noscript></a><br />\n这个世界很小，我们就这样遇见。这个世界很大，分开就很难再见。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3715.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3715.jpg\" alt=\"3715\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233440\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3715.jpg\" alt=\"3715\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233440\" /></noscript></a><br />\n当你不再急于否认错误时，你就学到了重要的一课。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3716.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3716.jpg\" alt=\"3716\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233441\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3716.jpg\" alt=\"3716\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233441\" /></noscript></a><br />\n此刻打盹，你将做梦；而此刻学习，你将圆梦。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3717.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3717.jpg\" alt=\"3717\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233442\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3717.jpg\" alt=\"3717\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233442\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我们不停的翻弄着回忆，却再也找不回那时的自己。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3718.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3718.jpg\" alt=\"3718\" width=\"500\" height=\"348\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233443\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3718.jpg\" alt=\"3718\" width=\"500\" height=\"348\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233443\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果这个片刻很美、很宁静，那么下一个片刻一定会更美、更宁静。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3719.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3719.jpg\" alt=\"3719\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233444\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3719.jpg\" alt=\"3719\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233444\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生命就像是一场徒步旅行，穿越荆棘和沼泽，我们终将会迎来最美的风景。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3720.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3720.jpg\" alt=\"3720\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233445\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3720.jpg\" alt=\"3720\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233445\" /></noscript></a><br />\n不要为别人怎么看你而烦恼。别人的看法并不重要，重要的是你怎么看待你自己。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1767),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>回来一段时间了，去过几次南昌。七月初去的时候，途径那座城市时还只是在全面整顿。再一次去，发现已整顿的差不多了，心里很是欢喜。统一的琉璃瓦，在阳光下闪闪发光。这座城市，印象中虽没有太多的情愫至于它，总以一个过客的微薄之情来看待它。但是，再一次遇见它时，对它有了感情，看一眼便忘不了的。<br />\n<span id=\"more-233355\"></span><br />\n这座城市有着它独特的魅力吸引着我，不是因为它的经济产业；陶瓷和货物运输，而是它的房子的风格，统一的琉璃瓦风格，给人一种很典雅的感觉。又像在对这个社会吐露着一种言语。也好像在诉说着这个城市的一种人文结合的文化，是那样和谐，团结。<br />\n自从喜欢上这个城市，途径它时，每每精神特好，它也好像有一种魔力，即使你前段时间还是在昏睡，但一途径它时，就精神特好，显然忘了途车劳累，也忘了一路颠簸的辛苦。<br />\n进入这个城市时，统一的琉璃瓦风格连你拒绝的时间都不给就已经跳入你的眼海，给你一种很温馨的感觉，之后再慢慢占入你的心，由心散漫至前身，有一种很霸道的占有欲，像在宣示；你的眼里只能有我。恰恰，这种宣示却让人无法拒绝。<br />\n很多时候，我很想把那种画面用手机把它拍摄下来，让它定格在那，也存点私心，让它仅仅属于我一个人。最后我还是已放弃作罢。因为我怕打扰它那种独特的美，也怕亵渎了它，也怕自己的拍摄技术而毁了它。<br />\n很喜欢这样的城市风格，也很为它而震撼。<br />\n去过几个地方，也见过它们的城市，但只有这个城市打动了我。希望它可以一直把它独特的美保留下去。<br />\n最后想起一句诗。我达达的马蹄，不是归人，只是个过客。或许就因为过客，才会想起你的美，才会念起吧！<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-thr