ass=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233161\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1431.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1431.jpg\" alt=\"1431\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233154\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1431.jpg\" alt=\"1431\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233154\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1437.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1437.jpg\" alt=\"1437\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233160\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1437.jpg\" alt=\"1437\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233160\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1436.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1436.jpg\" alt=\"1436\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233159\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1436.jpg\" alt=\"1436\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233159\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1435.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1435.jpg\" alt=\"1435\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233158\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1435.jpg\" alt=\"1435\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233158\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1434.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1434.jpg\" alt=\"1434\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-233157\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1434.jpg\" alt=\"1434\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-233157\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1771),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>闪耀的星辰像是历史遗留的光。寂寞而可爱,深沉而宁静。也许在我们面前生死都会远去。将近的岁月的抚摸带走活力,留下褶皱的细纹。老去是比死亡更可怕的事么。也许是的。因为怕年老终止思考,怕年老忘记美好,所以请耀眼的星辰替流逝的岁月甚至未来老去的我铭记你的容颜。<br />\n<span id=\"more-233089\"></span><br />\n也许现在相爱着依赖着的我们在未来的某一天不能在一起幸福,但起码拥有过那少时最纯净的梦抑或我的陪伴。虽然会有分离和悲凉,请允许当你老去时有我的影子,哪怕不是美好的影子,哪怕是泪水拼接的刹那,在星光铺满的夜空里我会祈祷我可以在你生命里存在,哪怕你会不允许。<br />\n不喜欢夜晚的黑暗却恋上星辰,那一颗颗挂在夜空的光亮是那样迷人。这最贪恋美感停止于白天望到被泛彩色微光拉长缩小的彩虹的一秒。那只是一片片叶子交替残留的空隙却好想呗停留在时间里,似钻石耀眼又 似珍珠透明,甚至藏有翡翠的清爽。仿佛世间一切美好都被吸引,无法清晰赞美出来又存在魅力。</p>\n<p>正悄悄在心里为你建一幢美丽的小屋。也许那里的装饰你并不喜欢：也许是违章建筑。但请慢慢欣赏改变的习惯。也让那颗厌倦玩闹的心重新推浪起瓦，让一切渐渐变成习惯现在，习惯我们的星空与爱。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.