></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript><a href=\'http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/71-21.jpg\' title=\'71-2\'><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/71-21-190x256.jpg\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"71-2\" /><noscript><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/71-21-190x256.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"71-2\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1778),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>当一个女人的嘴里反复出现一个男人的名字的时候，无论是夸那个男人还是骂那个男人，潜台词都是，我爱他。所以如果有人总念叨你，快从了吧。<br />\n<span id=\"more-232522\"></span><br />\n <a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/860.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/860.jpg\" alt=\"860\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232532\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/860.jpg\" alt=\"860\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232532\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我一直以为最糟糕的情况是你离开我，其实最令我难过的是你过得比我艰难。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/859.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/859.jpg\" alt=\"859\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232531\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/859.jpg\" alt=\"859\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232531\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生命中，有一个人可以去惦念，那是缘分；有一个人惦念着自己，是幸福。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/858.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/858.jpg\" alt=\"858\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232530\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/858.jpg\" alt=\"858\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232530\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果可以，我希望你是那个能陪我看过生命里所有日出日落的人.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/857.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/857.jpg\" alt=\"857\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232529\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/857.jpg\" alt=\"857\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232529\" /></noscript></a><br />\n我们都是在修补缺陷的过程中修行自己，了解自己，学习和别人相处，慢慢成长。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/856.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/856.jpg\" alt=\"856\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232528\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/856.jpg\" alt=\"856\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232528\" /></noscript></a><br />\n当一份幸福正在远离的时候 ，也是另一份幸福正在靠近当中 。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/855.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/855.jpg\" alt=\"855\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232527\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/855.jpg\" alt=\"855\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232527\" /></noscript></a><br />\n生命中总有那么一段时光，充满恐惧，可是除了勇敢面对，我们别无选择。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/854.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/854.jpg\" alt=\"854\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232526\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/854.jpg\" alt=\"854\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232526\" /></noscript></a><br />\n感情的债就和时光的海一样，都是我们越不过去的东西。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/853.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/853.jpg\" alt=\"853\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232525\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/853.jpg\" alt=\"853\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232525\" /></noscript></a><br />\n爱情一定是婚姻的前提，而珍惜，才是携手鬓白的那份必须的执念。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/852.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/852.jpg\" alt=\"852\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232524\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/852.jpg\" alt=\"852\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232524\" /></noscript></a><br />\n友谊和花香一样，还是淡一点的比较好，越淡的香气越使人依恋，也就越是让人难忘。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/851.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/851.jpg\" alt=\"851\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232523\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/851.jpg\" alt=\"851\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232523\" /></noscript></a><br />\n所谓青春， 就是可以无所畏惧地，去追想要的，无论什么。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1779),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>没有谁说过一生就只能爱一个人，亦没有谁说过，重新开始就是对过去的背叛。<br />\n<span id=\"more-232208\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/701.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/701.jpg\" alt=\"701\" width=\"500\" height=\"340\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232209\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/701.jpg\" alt=\"701\" width=\"500\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232209\" /></noscript></a><br />\n一句顺其自然，里面包含了我多少绝望和不甘心，如果你懂。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/702.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/702.jpg\" alt=\"702\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232210\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/702.jpg\" alt=\"702\" width=\"500\" height=\"330\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232210\" /></noscript></a><br />\n花一些时间，总会看清一些事。用一些事情，总会看清一些人。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/703.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/703.jpg\" alt=\"703\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232211\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/703.jpg\" alt=\"703\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232211\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人的一生会遭遇无数次相逢，有些人，是你看过便忘了的风景。有些人，则在你的心里生根抽芽。那些没有来由的缘分，缘深缘浅，早有分晓。之后任你我如何修行，也无法更改初时的模样。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/704.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/704.jpg\" alt=\"704\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232212\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/704.jpg\" alt=\"704\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232212\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果没有我，你是否别来无恙。如果没有你，告诉你，我不习惯。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/705.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/705.jpg\" alt=\"705\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232213\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/705.jpg\" alt=\"705\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232213\" /></noscript></a><br />\n失而复得的东西永远不会回到原来的样子<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/706.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/706.jpg\" alt=\"706\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232214\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/706.jpg\" alt=\"706\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232214\" /></noscript></a><br />\n当你知道了许多真实、虚假的东西，就没有那么多酸情了。你越来越沉默，越来越不想说。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/707.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/707.jpg\" alt=\"707\" width=\"500\" height=\"322\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232215\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/707.jpg\" alt=\"707\" width=\"500\" height=\"322\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232215\" /></noscript></a><br />\n人，一简单就快乐，但快乐的人寥寥无几；一复杂就痛苦，可痛苦的人却熙熙攘攘。这反映出的现实问题是：更多的人，要活出简单来不容易，要活出复杂来却很简单。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/708.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/708.jpg\" alt=\"708\" width=\"500\" height=\"511\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232216\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/708.jpg\" alt=\"708\" width=\"500\" height=\"511\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232216\" /></noscript></a><br />\n别妄想着倒带，这是生活，不是电影。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/709.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/709.jpg\" alt=\"709\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232217\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/709.jpg\" alt=\"709\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232217\" /></noscript></a><br />\n安全感，是尘埃落定的安稳，是不离不弃的笃信。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/710.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/710.jpg\" alt=\"710\" width=\"500\" height=\"348\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232218\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/710.jpg\" alt=\"710\" width=\"500\" height=\"348\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232218\" /></noscript></a><br />\n有些话，适合烂在心里，有些痛苦，适合无声无息的忘记。</p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1780),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>没安全感的人通常会觉得喜欢的人没有那么喜欢自己，一点小事就可以让不稳定的情绪爆发，之后在冷战中等待别人的让步，结果只会导致互不理睬不欢而散的下场，其实道歉并不一定代表自己真的错了，只是认为这段关系比自己的尊严更加重要，因为我更害怕对方的沉默不语，因为有时候我觉得沉默比争吵更加难熬。<br />\n<span id=\"more-232182\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/780.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/780.jpg\" alt=\"780\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232183\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/780.jpg\" alt=\"780\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232183\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/771.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/771.jpg\" alt=\"771\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232184\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/771.jpg\" alt=\"771\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232184\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/772.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/772.jpg\" alt=\"772\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232185\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/772.jpg\" alt=\"772\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232185\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/773.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/773.jpg\" alt=\"773\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232186\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/773.jpg\" alt=\"773\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232186\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/774.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/774.jpg\" alt=\"774\" width=\"500\" height=\"324\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232187\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/774.jpg\" alt=\"774\" width=\"500\" height=\"324\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232187\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/775.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/775.jpg\" alt=\"775\" width=\"500\" height=\"345\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232188\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/775.jpg\" alt=\"775\" width=\"500\" height=\"345\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232188\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/776.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/776.jpg\" alt=\"776\" width=\"500\" height=\"347\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232189\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/776.jpg\" alt=\"776\" width=\"500\" height=\"347\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232189\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/777.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/777.jpg\" alt=\"777\" width=\"500\" height=\"314\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232190\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/777.jpg\" alt=\"777\" width=\"500\" height=\"314\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232190\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/778.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/778.jpg\" alt=\"778\" width=\"500\" height=\"349\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232191\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/778.jpg\" alt=\"778\" width=\"500\" height=\"349\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232191\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/779.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/779.jpg\" alt=\"779\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-232192\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/779.jpg\" alt=\"779\" width=\"500\" height=\"329\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-232192\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1781),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>一个正青春的我，一定有一个正青春的你。<br />\n《滚滚红尘》里有一句歌词，“起初不经意的你　和少年不经事的我”。用这句歌词来形容我们，不是风情恰好？<br />\n你一定曾经遇到过这样的男孩子……<span id=\"more-232424\"></span><br />\n他陪你哭，陪你笑，陪你伤心，陪你沉默。你还记得吗，他曾经在你流泪哭泣的时候，默默地陪着你，看着你；他的身边永远有用不完的餐巾纸，但你却不知道为什么，问他的时候，他只是淡淡的笑笑，说是自己鼻涕多；他爱好体育运动，尤其是打篮球，他在篮球场上的英姿，朝气蓬勃，你会为他呐喊、助威，当他投进第一个球的时候，会把视线移向你，你朝他竖起了大拇指，他对你傻乎乎地笑。<br />\n那个时候，你的文科好，他的理科好，两个人时常互相问问题，讨论学习，会比谁的成绩好，自然，你们走得很近，于是，八卦、绯闻就来了，老师也听说了，老师苦口婆心的教育你们，你们却一副无所谓的样子？为的什么？是出于对对方的信任和对自己的笃定，你确信，他确信，这是纯友情。<br />\n那个时候，你是个爱哭鬼，连英语重默这种小事，对于你这个要求完美的处女座来说，也是个很大的打击，午睡的时候，你趴在桌子上，尽力让背看起来没有多大的起伏，可终究还是被他发现了，于是，他偷偷地递过来一张便利签，上面画着你最爱的工藤新一和怪盗基德，虽然很丑，却让你笑了，上面还写着，“今晚我会来偷走你所有的作业”，现在想想，那是个多么拙劣的玩笑。<br />\n那个时候，你最爱喝草莓味道的酸牛奶，每次运动会上，做后勤的都是他，他拎回来的一大袋子饮料里，总有两罐格格不入的草莓味酸牛奶，这时候，你总会拍拍他的肩膀，“谢谢哥儿们”，他也会回敬你，“不用谢，兄弟”。<br />\n那个时候，快要中考了，你们曾经打赌，谁的成绩没有另一个人的好，就要给对方买一百盒阿华田，结果，你输了，他考上了省里的中点高中，你上了市里的重点。他总是打电话“追杀”你，“一百盒阿华田呢？”老掉牙的开场白，你每次都笑嘻嘻地赖掉，他也不以为意。只是，你们好像有什么不对了，是否，是那两算学校的距离，让你们有了隔阂？<br />\n进了高中，课业繁忙，和他联系的越来越少，只是，你有种极其不适应的感觉，为什么？你说不上来，只是，你哭泣的时候没了餐巾纸，你做作业的时候没了讨论的对象，只是篮球场上没了那个眼神和傻乎乎的笑，没人再把新一和基德画的那么丑……你不习惯，很不习惯。<br />\n你觉得有点想他了，恩，有点，真的只是有点吗？真的只是想念么？你说，你不知道。<br />\n后来，高一寒假，你们总算见到面了，他更从容洒脱，少了几分少年的稚气，而你自己，却看上去依旧没怎么变，半年的想念，貌似一下子沉寂了，心，静了。<br />\n当他笑嘻嘻地走过来，对你说，“嘿，兄弟”时，你拍了拍他的肩膀，“嘿，哥儿们”。依旧如初中一样，貌似那半年的疏远，都是不存在的。你们那天聊了很多，学习、生活，包括感情。<br />\n他对你说，他有了一个很喜欢的女孩子……他还说了很多，只是你听不进去了，你感觉，你的胸口闷闷的，鼻子酸酸的，有种窒息的感觉。为什么？<br />\n最后，他拍拍你的肩膀“兄弟，我先走了，拜拜”。简短的一句话，结束了这一天。只是，他不知道，在他缓缓离开的时候，你的目光一直注视着他，直到他的背影模糊，消失……<br />\n一滴眼泪，顺着脸颊缓缓地流下来，嘴巴尝到了，是无尽的苦涩，涩到了心里，骨头里。<br />\n那是暗恋的味道，那是成长的滋味。<br />\n诶，那时的少年，你一定会说，我曾经喜欢过你。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hi