想了好久，决定去哪里。<br />\n我疯狂的爱上那片阳光明媚的海，很偏很偏。<br />\n我讲的故事，你有没有听过。<br />\n我不回来几次，旧装换上新装。<br />\n天快亮了，你是否醒了。<br />\n最朴素的生活与最遥远的梦想。<br />\n她的曾经，一定很快乐。<br />\n有阳光的味道。<br />\n我们不是只有现在吗。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/image