n flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript><a href=\'http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/43aeabd5gw1e7maobjm1sj20b20gomyc.jpg\' title=\'43aeabd5gw1e7maobjm1sj20b20gomyc\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/43aeabd5gw1e7maobjm1sj20b20gomyc-300x300.jpg\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden attachment-onehalfsquare-inpost\" alt=\"43aeabd5gw1e7maobjm1sj20b20gomyc\" /><noscript><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/43aeabd5gw1e7maobjm1sj20b20gomyc-300x300.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onehalfsquare-inpost\" alt=\"43aeabd5gw1e7maobjm1sj20b20gomyc\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1791),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>就要结束了。</p>\n<p>也曾经想象一切落下帷幕会是怎样的心情。可是，来的太快，让人措手不及。<br />\n<span id=\"more-231455\"></span><br />\n就算是夏天，也喜欢阳光的日子。哪怕叶子都要被烤焦，哪怕被反射的阳光亮的让人睁不开眼，哪怕涂了防晒霜还是会被晒黑。</p>\n<p>雨天太潮湿。心潮湿。眼也潮湿。其实，也只不过是太矫情的错觉。</p>\n<p>不断的走走停停，兜兜转转。得到了什么，又失去了什么。学会了什么，又懂得了什么。<br />\n对这些我都没有概念。只是，觉得，时光只自顾自的走，我在原地乱了阵脚。表现出的迷茫与彷徨的姿态让人发笑。</p>\n<p>理发师只是觉得剪掉的是头发，他却不知道，那是我们蓄了很久的时光。蓄了很久的，很久的，很久的记忆。<br />\n一缕缕落地，一丝丝回忆。<br />\n像是看破红尘的僧人。喜怒哀乐都失去了意义。</p>\n<p>你听见飞机隆隆的飞过天空。<br />\n是多少人在上面哭泣。要离开，不想离开，不得不离开，想离开，迫不及待离开。无数种离开方式，无数种情感，无数种……</p>\n<p>就算是夏天，还是，还是会有凉凉的风。它吹过你的脸颊，它让你的裙摆轻轻荡漾，它让你的心情稍稍舒畅。它是风，属于你的微风，哪里都存在。</p>\n<p>你是静静地听一首歌吗？你有静静地看一本书吗。你有偷偷地想过去，然后，只能再绝望的想未来吗？没有，也没有关系，这样得感觉，从来不会是幸福。</p>\n<p>或许每个人都期待开始。可是，有的人却惧怕开始。我没有期待，也没有惧怕。我只是知道就要开始了而已。这样静静地知道了就好了。不想其他任何。</p>\n<p>曲曲折折的来路，曲曲折折的去路。回头看看那些弯弯的路。苦笑着说，真美好。再看看前面那长长的崎岖的路途，打个寒战，还是硬着头皮走下去。哪怕是一个人。</p>\n<p>天空雾蒙蒙的从来不招我喜欢。<br />\n我也真是天真，它为什么要讨我喜欢呢。<br />\n我想要的阳光从来不是那样轻易得到。</p>\n<p>我也逐渐看得清楚。我也渐渐在雾蒙蒙的天空下活的自在。<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\