/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript></noscript><a href=\'http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/9195013451_7ca7c9bb80_b.jpg\' title=\'9195013451_7ca7c9bb80_b\'><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/9195013451_7ca7c9bb80_b-190x256.jpg\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"9195013451_7ca7c9bb80_b\" /><noscript><img width=\"190\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/9195013451_7ca7c9bb80_b-190x256.jpg\" class=\"attachment-onethirdportrait-inpost\" alt=\"9195013451_7ca7c9bb80_b\" /></noscript></a></dt><dd>&nbsp;</dd></dl><div class=\"duotive-gallery-separator\">',1794),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>如果你的人生可以重来，你一定不想认识我吧。是我，将你的人生搞得一团乱，因为不甘心一个人痛苦，不甘心就这样沉默地忍耐你的谎言，所以说了许多决绝的话，像个疯子一样，愚蠢又可笑。</p>\n<p>如果你的人生可以重来，你一定不要认识我。不要对我微笑，不要对我好，不要说冬天要多穿衣服，不要问我吃了饭没有，不要说担心我，不要在过马路的时候牵我的手，就让那个寂寞的人一直寂寞。</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-231185\"></span><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143251eg9hi01rnt1fnlnd.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143251eg9hi01rnt1fnlnd.jpg\" alt=\"143251eg9hi01rnt1fnlnd\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231186\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143251eg9hi01rnt1fnlnd.jpg\" alt=\"143251eg9hi01rnt1fnlnd\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231186\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果你的人生可以重来，如果不小心对我微笑了，你一定要马上转身，以遥远又得体的距离慢慢收起你的笑容，我会以为只是一刹那的错觉而无动于衷，而寂寞的人会一直寂寞，但不会疼痛。</p>\n<p>如果你的人生可以重来，如果不小心对我微笑了，问我为什么穿得这么少，那么一定要用一种客套的语气，这样，我就会以为，这只是人与人之间普通的礼节，而这个寂寞的人会一直寂寞，但不会哭泣。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143249at66kh5ky75tr2fw.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143249at66kh5ky75tr2fw.jpg\" alt=\"143249at66kh5ky75tr2fw\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231189\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143249at66kh5ky75tr2fw.jpg\" alt=\"143249at66kh5ky75tr2fw\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231189\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果你的人生可以重来，如果不了心握了我的手，请不要表现得那么深情，那么我就不会以为这种手心的温度就是一生，而这个寂寞的人，会一直寂寞，但不会在半夜醒来哭着提醒自己好好活下去。</p>\n<p>如果你的人生可以重来，如果在过马路的时候以保护的姿势牵了我的手，在日晒雨淋的季节，用整个雨伞帮我阻挡了酷暑与寒冷，那么，不要再想着转身，好好爱这个寂寞的人，珍惜她的余生。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143247flgthgg3gtff8gj0.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143247flgthgg3gtff8gj0.jpg\" alt=\"143247flgthgg3gtff8gj0\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231188\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143247flgthgg3gtff8gj0.jpg\" alt=\"143247flgthgg3gtff8gj0\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231188\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果你的人生可重来，如果对我起了誓言，那么就要一直遵守，不要辜负我，不要背叛我，不要让这个寂寞的人，以为人生就是每夜每夜的哭泣，不要让这个努力像向日葵一样活过来的人，重新变成夜里不曾见过阳光就枯萎的昙花。</p>\n<p>如果你的人生可以重来，如果在重来之前知道不能守护这个人一辈子，那么就一定不要开始，因为一旦开始，即使仅仅是一个微笑，那个寂寞又认真的人已经赔了她的一生。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143249kxa2xxpajhmeppjh.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143249kxa2xxpajhmeppjh.jpg\" alt=\"143249kxa2xxpajhmeppjh\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231190\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143249kxa2xxpajhmeppjh.jpg\" alt=\"143249kxa2xxpajhmeppjh\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231190\" /></noscript></a><br />\n如果你的人生可重来，我对你来说，只是你人生那么小的一部分，那么，试着忽略吧，装作不认识，我不过是你在那样无聊的时候遇到的一个过客。但如果你走近后又离开，那个寂寞的人会一直留在原处，所以，如果你的人生可以重来，那么在走过她身旁的时候，请一步也不要停留。</p>\n<p>如果你的人生可以重来，为了我，请不要来到我所在的城市，看尽所有灯火后，留给这个寂寞的人一片黑漆漆的天空。</p>\n<p> <a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143246hz11v1wj7vl92xf1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143246hz11v1wj7vl92xf1.jpg\" alt=\"143246hz11v1wj7vl92xf1\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231187\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/143246hz11v1wj7vl92xf1.jpg\" alt=\"143246hz11v1wj7vl92xf1\" width=\"510\" height=\"340\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231187\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1795),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>我不能说一辈子只能爱一个人，这根本不可能。可是一定有一个人，能让我笑得最灿烂，哭得最透彻，记的最深刻。<br />\n<span id=\"more-231144\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2511.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2511.jpg\" alt=\"251\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231145\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2511.jpg\" alt=\"251\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231145\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2521.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2521.jpg\" alt=\"252\" width=\"500\" height=\"266\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231146\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2521.jpg\" alt=\"252\" width=\"500\" height=\"266\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231146\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2531.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2531.jpg\" alt=\"253\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231147\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2531.jpg\" alt=\"253\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231147\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2541.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2541.jpg\" alt=\"254\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231148\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2541.jpg\" alt=\"254\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231148\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2551.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2551.jpg\" alt=\"255\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231149\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2551.jpg\" alt=\"255\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231149\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2561.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2561.jpg\" alt=\"256\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231150\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2561.jpg\" alt=\"256\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231150\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2571.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2571.jpg\" alt=\"257\" width=\"400\" height=\"268\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231151\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2571.jpg\" alt=\"257\" width=\"400\" height=\"268\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231151\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2581.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2581.jpg\" alt=\"258\" width=\"500\" height=\"298\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231152\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2581.jpg\" alt=\"258\" width=\"500\" height=\"298\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231152\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2591.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2591.jpg\" alt=\"259\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231153\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2591.jpg\" alt=\"259\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231153\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2601.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2601.jpg\" alt=\"260\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-231154\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2601.jpg\" alt=\"260\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-231154\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1796),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>在这个年代文艺小清新似乎异常地受到追捧。之前闺蜜就在我耳边叨着《致青春》有多感人至深，由于各种情由我错过时机。偶然发现电脑也可以看，就想去一探究竟。<br />\n<span id=\"more-231076\"></span><br />\n我是一个从来不会把内心掏出来的人，周围不解的人就会觉得我清高，懂我的人知道我内心那股热火。我不知道自己怎么会突然说道这个，看过之后就在脑海中飘起。那些年我们的懵懂，我们的憧憬，似乎渐行远离，想拿个瓶子把她藏起来，可惜后来谁都没能如愿以偿。我们还在若无其事地假装平静，假装还年轻，骗自己那些年的我们依旧。骄纵自己肆意妄为，却不知道举手投足间，年华已随风而逝，而我们还是假装不以为然。是不是永远都是这样，小的时候渴望成人世界，长大后又想回到小时候。只是我们再也回不去了，我们彼此见证的青春，大概过得很好吧。我们没有停下来的机会，回首当年的青涩，除了一笑而过，应该找不到其它更好的方式。很多年后，我还在继续缅怀。那些年陪在我身边的你们，过得好吗？<br />\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><dl class=\'duotive-gallery-item\'><dt class=\'gallery-icon pageflip\'><span class=\"icon icon-zoom\">&nbsp;</span><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fqp-three/images/page_flip.png\" /><noscript><img class=\"lazy lazy-hidden flip\" src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/themes/fq