/noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1802),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>蛋形建筑（exbury egg）位于英国beaulieu河口，它既是一个住宅，又能当研究潮溪的实验室，是一个拥有完整储藏区和展示区的收集整理中心。设计师利用船舶的制造技术和当地材料来建造这个蛋形空间，其内部包括一张床、一个桌子、小火炉和一个湿房间。这个蛋像船一样被“固定”在摇篮式的结构中，会随着潮汐上下起伏。它还可通过太阳能为各种电器充电。<br />\n<span id=\"more-230109\"></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_02.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_02.jpg\" alt=\"exbury_egg_02\" width=\"500\" height=\"452\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-230110\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_02.jpg\" alt=\"exbury_egg_02\" width=\"500\" height=\"452\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-230110\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_03.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_03.jpg\" alt=\"exbury_egg_03\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-230111\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_03.jpg\" alt=\"exbury_egg_03\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-230111\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_04.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/exbury_egg_04.jpg\" alt=\"exbury_egg_04\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-230112\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://w