t=\"331\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-230102\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_3_1373089603_c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b1.jpg\" alt=\"img_3_1373089603_c4ca4238a0b923820dcc509a6f75849b\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-230102\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_4_1373089603_14ecb9ef89c875d10d334bef25c046a51.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_4_1373089603_14ecb9ef89c875d10d334bef25c046a51.jpg\" alt=\"img_4_1373089603_14ecb9ef89c875d10d334bef25c046a5\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-230103\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_4_1373089603_14ecb9ef89c875d10d334bef25c046a51.jpg\" alt=\"img_4_1373089603_14ecb9ef89c875d10d334bef25c046a5\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-230103\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_5_1373089603_b12e07bceb5588f93ff386e7713741c21.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_5_1373089603_b12e07bceb5588f93ff386e7713741c21.jpg\" alt=\"Print\" width=\"500\" height=\"386\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-230104\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_5_1373089603_b12e07bceb5588f93ff386e7713741c21.jpg\" alt=\"Print\" width=\"500\" height=\"386\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-230104\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_7_1373089603_20edb848504454f3a2118b690244132c.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_7_1373089603_20edb848504454f3a2118b690244132c.jpg\" alt=\"img_7_1373089603_20edb848504454f3a2118b690244132c\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-230105\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/img_7_1373089603_20edb848504454f3a2118b690244132c.jpg\" alt=\"img_7_1373089603_20edb848504454f3a2118b690244132c\" width=\"500\" height=\"331\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-230105\" /></noscript></a></p>\n                                    <!--end of entry content -->\r\n                ',1804),('‘’','‘’','\r\n                    <p>《Nachtfluge》是美国风光摄影师Kevin Cooley拍摄的一组照片。他通过长时间曝光的方法，在美国各地机场拍摄下飞机轨迹划过天空的精彩照片。Cooley在美国几个主要机场进行拍摄，包括洛杉矶的LAX，纽约的JFK和EWR，以及北卡罗来纳的ETC等。<br />\n<span id=\"more-222965\"></span><br />\n这些照片使用林哈夫Technikardan 45s 4×5相机和施耐德135mm Apo Sysmmar镜头拍摄。拍摄光圈收缩到f/22，曝光时间通常为4-5分钟。Cooley说道：“摄影本来就和时间密切相关。快门既可以捕捉到眨眼的瞬间，也可以，像这组照片一样，将数分钟甚至数小时的时间收入一张画面中。”<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/5201.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/5201.jpg\" alt=\"520\" width=\"499\" height=\"389\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-full wp-image-222966\" /><noscript><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/5201.jpg\" alt=\"520\" width=\"499\" height=\"389\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-222966\" /></noscript></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/5111.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/plugins/bj-lazy-load/img/placeholder.gif\" data-lazy-type=\"image\" data-lazy-src=\"http://www.fqpai.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/5111.jpg\" alt=\"511\" width=\"499\" height=\"389\" class=\"lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-f